description: Have dinner ready in no time with this quick vegetarian recipe which teams sticky, smoky kebabs with a refreshing quinoa salad.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Gluten free,Spring,Video,Low sugar,Nov 2020,Sesame free,Microwave,High protein,High fibre,Soy free,Wheat free,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: Quick Sticky Vegetable Kebabs With Quinoa Salad Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 750g BBQ vegetable kebab kit with smokey BBQ marinade

recipeInstructions.text: Rinse quinoa. Place in a large microwave-safe bowl. Add 2 cups water. Cover and microwave on high for 5 minutes. Stir. Microwave on medium for 2 minutes. Stand for 2 minutes.
Meanwhile, thread vegetables onto pre- soaked bamboo skewers, reserving marinade.
Heat a greased barbecue grill or chargrill pan over high heat. Cook skewers, turning and brushing with reserved marinade, for 8 minutes or until tender and starting to char.
Place salad kit in a bowl, adding walnuts and feta and reserving dressing. Add quinoa and parsley. Toss to combine. Divide among plates. Top with skewers and drizzle with dressing. Serve.
